<C>__{ray}
<D>__{how much extra?}
<C>__{kyle}
<P>__{(calling out)}
<D>__{he wants the tv option, dusty.}
<C>__{rhodes}
<D>__{i reckon i can hear him. tv option, that's a dollar twenty, makes nine eighty six plus tax.}
<C>__{kyle}
