<A>__{"looking at this scene now, years later, it strikes us that revising it out of existence, as we did, constituted too much rewriting. indeed, the more prosaic scene we replaced it with, involving ray stopped at a traffic light, can be found in the finished script but not in the finished movie. it was shot but then deleted in order to more quickly get to the carnage, which was the picture's raison d' etre..."}
